{% comment %} TSQ Heritage / About section {% endcomment %}
<section class="tsq-heritage-section">
  <div class="tsq-heritage-inner">
    <div class="tsq-heritage-label">Our Heritage</div>
    <h2 class="tsq-heritage-title">Born in Australia.<br>Inspired by the East.</h2>
    <div class="tsq-heritage-rule"></div>
    <div class="tsq-heritage-body">
      <p>The Scent Quarter was founded by a group of fragrance lovers right here in Australia who fell deeply in love with the art of Middle Eastern perfumery. What started as a personal obsession — seeking out rare oud blends, smoky orientals, and luminous florals from the world's great Arabian fragrance houses — became a mission to share these extraordinary scents with fellow Australians.</p>
      <p>We curate directly from the most respected houses in the Gulf: Lattafa, Afnan, Rasasi, Armaf, Gissah and more. Each fragrance is authentic, each decant is hand-poured with care. We believe you shouldn't have to commit to a full bottle to discover your signature scent — which is why we make it possible to experience world-class Arabian perfumery from just $15.</p>
      <p>This is not just retail. It's a passion project rooted in culture, craftsmanship, and community. Welcome to The Scent Quarter.</p>
    </div>
    <a href="/collections/all-decants" class="tsq-heritage-cta">Explore Our Collection →</a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.tsq-heritage-section {
  background: var(--tsq-champagne, #EFE5D2);
  padding: 80px 20px;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--tsq-stone, #D8C9B6);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--tsq-stone, #D8C9B6);
}
.tsq-heritage-inner {
  max-width: 680px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  text-align: center;
}
.tsq-heritage-label {
  font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
  font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  color: var(--tsq-gold, #C6A15B); text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.tsq-heritage-title {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 44px; color: var(--tsq-charcoal, #1B1917);
  font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.15;
  margin: 0 0 20px;
}
.tsq-heritage-rule {
  width: 48px; height: 1px;
  background: var(--tsq-gold, #C6A15B); margin: 0 auto 28px;
}
.tsq-heritage-body p {
  font-family: 'Lora', serif;
  font-size: 16px !important; line-height: 1.8 !important;
  color: var(--tsq-mocha, #7B6652) !important;
  margin: 0 0 18px !important;
  text-align: left;
}
.tsq-heritage-cta {
  display: inline-block; margin-top: 12px;
  font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
  font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.14em;
  text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--tsq-charcoal, #1B1917) !important;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(27,25,23,0.3);
  padding-bottom: 2px;
  text-decoration: none !important;
}
.tsq-heritage-cta:hover { color: var(--tsq-gold, #C6A15B) !important; border-color: rgba(198,161,91,0.5); }
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "TSQ Heritage",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "shopify-section"
}
{% endschema %}
